{"tid":2032131,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"醉酒後酒醒 驚見兩位好兄弟和女友客廳3P 23歲仔失望淚奔","createTime":"2020-05-24T01:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T05:11:42.000Z","uid":54373,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"30ba87bd643154bd46d2a2989f62395f32590150","tid":2032131,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:36:11.000Z","msg":"打孖上真係好難頂<br />\n<br />\n日前，外國一名網民大吐苦水，稱自己被兩名好友戴綠帽，二人竟趁著他飲大咗時「搞阿嫂」，和他的女友在客廳「激戰」，目睹現場的他氣得奪門而出。事後女友雖然曾多次尋求原諒，朋友們亦深感後悔，但他還是無法邁過這道坎。<br />\n<br />\n（Getty設計圖片）<br />\n<br />\n據報導，一名23歲的男子表示，自己跟20歲女友到朋友家慶生，甚至預早計畫好留宿一晚。當晚，他果然玩得相當盡興，更多喝了幾杯，最後不勝酒力，便告訴女友，自己要上樓睡一覺。<br />\n<br />\n（Getty設計圖片）<br />\n<br />\n然而就在他睡醒之後，卻發現女友不在身邊，於是下樓倒杯水並且尋找女友。未料卻發現其兩名好兄弟，竟在樓下跟女友激情親熱！三人看到他出現的時候都嚇呆了，而他則因為無法接受衝擊性畫面，竟衝上樓瘋狂嘔吐，接著換好衣服含淚奔回家。<br />\n<br />\n（Getty設計圖片）<br />\n<br />\n女友事後曾發訊息哀求他的原諒，但是至此之後他已經難過得不願再見到她；兩位朋友之後也給他發訊息道歉。<br />\n<br />\n該網友悲傷表示，雖然很難過，但是一想到那畫面就覺得噁心，「到時候回到工作崗位還要遇到他們兩個」，所幸公司答應調班，盡可能避免尷尬的場面出現。<br />\n<br />\n（Getty設計圖片）<br />\n<br />\n不少網友看到之後得感到十分震驚，大多都留言安慰他不要難過，「酒精永遠都不是藉口」、「一次兩個，兄弟你確定不要緊吧？」、「太可憐了」、「千萬不能心軟！」、「你還年輕，趕緊分手」，「下一個更好」。"},{"pid":"550754d6e0061788e3a5e8659574ade1e776f1dd","tid":2032131,"uid":62850,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:40:36.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3bc6a264b2117c9f4cdc6e1632e25524d830a00","tid":2032131,"uid":95,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:42:13.000Z","msg":"竟然無圖！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ede450cc49ba38845a61a52a6a64ccd5a69856a","tid":2032131,"uid":203057,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:43:36.000Z","msg":"（Getty設計圖片）"},{"pid":"2807c2ad2981e05f395ecbf0450ca00db9ea087a","tid":2032131,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:45:30.000Z","msg":"個兩個好兄弟互射左幾多次"},{"pid":"fe7de65872edb4d97d39f828f4aaca87f8da223c","tid":2032131,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"550754d6e0061788e3a5e8659574ade1e776f1dd","tid":2032131,"uid":62850,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:40:36.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:46:09.000Z","msg":"你估香港冇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b476f913f9d1a8b30f44b6f1743987daffc21941","tid":2032131,"uid":277381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:48:11.000Z","msg":"大家想做邊個？"},{"pid":"98aff56f51d76696f1159b497a52640a52f48b29","tid":2032131,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b476f913f9d1a8b30f44b6f1743987daffc21941","tid":2032131,"uid":277381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:48:11.000Z","msg":"大家想做邊個？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:56:41.000Z","msg":"條女"},{"pid":"c83a1a358bbb8b2df171f1e7cca5a25628ef971d","tid":2032131,"uid":1734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:59:34.000Z","msg":"主角係六日子 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1ad75da72cfa522dc3171c1d32b82ed3648f24","tid":2032131,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:01:08.000Z","msg":"Pr公司post 拉"},{"pid":"5aa6d1efa97d734d996e464f55eee5cb5593a0f9","tid":2032131,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c83a1a358bbb8b2df171f1e7cca5a25628ef971d","tid":2032131,"uid":1734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:59:34.000Z","msg":"主角係六日子 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/